{
 "name": "RPlog_Ghastly_Gala",
 "title": "Ghastly Gala",
 "summary": "At Castle Tsabak on Dreven, the fashion designer Zubindi Hakoon throws a grotesque gala -- 'Grotesques and Odalisques' -- to fete the duality of the dead bioterrorist Basca Starker, whose preserved clone lies on an altar. The macabre, black-and-white-themed event draws the droid Cricket, the tattooed Biscuit Baron heiress Atsvara, the physician Lynae Cassius, the impassive Falleen Ssanyu, and the chipper holojournalist Nara Rhen, among many lesion-ridden Xa Fel waiters and exotic 'odalisque' models. The Sith Imperator Malign arrives in mock-Jedi robes with his apprentice Quaye and a comic squad of mutant-Wookiee guards, prompting Cricket to subject him to a humiliating 'sock check.' A drunken blaze bug's amorous pursuit of Nara's camdroid causes a comic uproar until the droid V1C3 arrests it, and the partygoers -- joined by the smooth-talking Tray Garos and the escort-turned-entrepreneur Vanilla -- trade gossip about Starker's crimes, the absent host Malif, and the bizarre spectacle around them.",
